                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17950218-22-off108 t17950218-22-cd109"></join>, and burglariously stealing therein, a tin cannister, value 100. one pound and four ounces weight of black tea, value 4s. and four pounds of starch, value 2s.
            </rs> the goods of the said 
               <persName id="t17950218-22-person294">
